headline: Thornburg International Equity Fund Q1 2025 Commentary
summary: In 1Q25, the portfolio (I share class) returned 9.92%, 469 basis points ahead of the MSCI ACWI ex-U.S. Index and 992 basis points ahead of the MSCI EAFE Index.
